As a gamer
I want to be able to put games that i am interested in getting into a list
so that i can make better decisions on what games to get

As a gamer 
i want to be able to right notes on my opinions on games that i have played
so that i can organise my thoughts better

as a game reviewer
i want to be able to post all of my reviews to one site
so that people can see them all more clearly
